onsiderably sharper in the SCM than in other models, indicating an incipient\ninstability of the system according to this model. We also study the\ndistribution of charges induced by a charged particle grazing over a SIM\nsurface at constant speed. This distribution is shown to contain model-specific\nfeatures that are of immediate experimental interest.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 21 Jun 2018 16:20:04 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 22 Jun 2018 20:34:33 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Sun, 22 Jul 2018 09:35:42 GMT"},{"version":"v4","created":"Mon, 13 Aug 2018 10:19:37 GMT"},{"version":"v5","created":"Fri, 1 Feb 2019 13:47:59 GMT"},{"version":"v6","created":"Sun, 10 May 2020 10:31:20 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-05-12"}
