oduce a notion of {\\it\nsemi-temperedness}, which is much weaker than temperedness, but allows for the\ndeduction of the main result without any hypothesis whatsoever on $K/F$.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 21 Jun 2018 21:34:36 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-06-25"}
