e\nproposed method has more effectiveness and versatility than many\nstate-of-the-art approaches.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 22 Jun 2018 06:48:07 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 10 Jul 2018 02:45:39 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-07-11"}
