au-Lifshitz equation, and Monte Carlo simulations. As promising candidates\nto observe the clustering states, we revisit the origin of \"spin molecules\"\nobserved in a family of spinel oxides $AB_2$O$_4$ ($A=$ Zn, Hg, Mg, $B=$ Cr,\nFe).\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 22 Jun 2018 07:55:00 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 6 Nov 2018 02:59:51 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-11-07"}
